## .NET Performance Analysis — `CaseTransformExtensions.cs`

**Scan Execution Checklist:**

| Recipe | Hits |
|--------|------|
| `RegexOptions.Compiled` | 7 (3 conditional + 3 unconditional + 1 per-instance) |
| `[GeneratedRegex]` | 3 (correct, .NET 7+ only) |
