- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for .NET 7+ (lines 13, 16, 19)
- ✅ Conditional compilation cleanly separates .NET 7+ source-gen from pre-7 compiled regex
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()`
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` and `WordCount` use manual iteration — zero allocations
